      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.681904602
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.931904602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "以前、千紗やこころ、すずと特別ライブをしただろう？\n今回はすみれに、ソロでお願いしたいって話でな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_church-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "church-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.8438093185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "覚えてます、凄く荘厳な雰囲気で……懐かしいな～\nあの時の衣装がまた着られるなんて、嬉しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6104759852,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10842.564257,
          "startTime": 47.4530402422
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4604764938
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4604764938
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1748527527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "今回も、凄く綺麗なセットで撮影予定なんですね\nそれに……ピアノかパイプオルガンの伴奏付き？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1748527527,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9039.6065663,
          "startTime": 56.214459319
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "生演奏で歌えるなんて凄く嬉しいです！　収録日は……\nえぇっ！？　こ、この日は……うーん……でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9413466602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9438098271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、すみれ\nその日は何か予定が入ってるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8215472475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、大きな声出しちゃってすみません\nえっと……個人的なことで申し訳ないんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.6475281397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.5808619816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "この日、山形の中学校で授業参観があるんです\n私、お仕事で授業参観の日は休んでばかりでしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.980861473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8808619816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "だから今回は、両親が張り切って二人で来てくれるって\n言ってくれてて……私も楽しみにしてたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5475281397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5808619816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……それは大切な予定だな。分かった\n収録の時間を後ろにずらしてもらえるよう、調整するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3527665455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　それなら授業参観とお仕事\n両方とも参加出来るでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2219557445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0527665455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "移動のスケジュールがタイトになりそうだけど\n多分大丈夫だ。当日は、俺も精一杯サポートするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがサポートしてくれるなら\n心強いです！　私も時間厳守で頑張りますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7280041057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4613379477
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "山形で、授業参観に両親が来てくれて\nその後は東京で、私の単独ライブ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7946707724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.894671281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか凄く豪華な一日ですね！\nこれで伴奏がお兄ちゃんだったら完璧なのにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9946707724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.7280046144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて、えへへ、つい欲張っちゃいました\n今のは忘れて下さい。……あれ？　どうかしました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3613374391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　いや、別に、なんでもないよ？　……えっと\nすみれのお兄さんはピアノ、今も続けてるんだっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.2273247717
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　それで、お兄ちゃんがピアノでデビューしたら\n一緒のステージに立つのが私の夢なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9939909297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.160658105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか～。すみれはお兄さんが大好きだもんな\nその時は、俺も頑張って仕事を取ってこないとな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.9572571116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、考えただけで幸せになれます……！\nなんだか、どんどんやる気が溢れてきました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.0239232697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.8239237783
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そろそろ次のお仕事に向かわないと\n{user}さん、ありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.8905899363,
