      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……うぅ～！　……あ、{user}さん\nお疲れ様です……うるさくしちゃってすみません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.4092688222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、すみれ？　その、お疲れ様……\nそれで、何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "その、実は……授業参観の日に、どうしても外せない\nお仕事が入って、両親が来られなくなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.2106581685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "凄く残念ですけど……お仕事じゃ仕方ないですよね\nだから、お兄ちゃんに来てくれないか聞いてみたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 256.6439915018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら急にそわそわして「その日は東京で用事だ！」\nって……なんの用事かも教えてくれないんですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.7811546937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "（そ、それは……！）\n（ドッキリの仕事だから言えなかったんだな……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "なんでって聞いても「すみれにはまだ早い」って……\n子供扱いするなんて失礼だと思いませんか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.5451255478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
