      "text": "（確かに、ドッキリのネタばらしにはまだ早い……！）\n（山形のお兄さん、苦しい返しをさせてすみません……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.6487221569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "お兄ちゃん……もしかして、何か内緒にしてる……？\n私の知らないうちに……まさか東京で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.586048275,
      "sfxList": []
