      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな～。すみれも東京で仕事をしてるんだし\n恋人が出来たなら、そのうち紹介してくれるかもな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.2667032879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……でも妹の私より、恋人の方が大事なんだ\n私の授業参観はその日だけなのになぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.9989492573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr024.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ、お兄ちゃんのバカ\n一週間は口利いてあげないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.7989492573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "（ご両親のことはともかく、お兄さんについては）\n（俺にも責任がある……すみません、お兄さん……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 337.5000366212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
