      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ……良かったら俺が授業参観に行ってもいいか？\nすみれの通っている中学校も見てみたいしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.2667032879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr025.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか！？\nで、でも……山形まで来てもらわないといけないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 351.2876794971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。その後の東京の仕事にも\nアテンドしやすいしな。マネージャーとしても助かる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 358.4667032879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr026.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、{user}さんが来てくれるなんて！\nありがとうございます！　じゃあ約束ですよっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.2144822276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr027.m4a",
      "text": "ゆーびきーりげんまんっ♪　嘘つーいたーら\nはーり千本飲ーますっ♪　指切った♪",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 375.4478155609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-smr028.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと子供っぽかったでしょうか、えへへ……。でも\n私には東京にもお兄ちゃんがいるって、ほっとしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 386.5811468597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、任せてくれ。授業参観、俺も楽しみにしているよ\n朝からだろうし、前日のうちに一緒に山形に向かおうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 396.63336792,
      "sfxList": []
